ower laws. Different components can be associated\nto acceleration/cooling processes taking place in the jet. The reconstruction\nof FSRQs also incorporates a QSO-like component to account for the BLR, plus a\nvery steep power law, associated to the accretion disk.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Feb 2022 19:00:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-02"}
