imit as general relativity will still possess non-equatorial constant-$r$\ngeodesics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Feb 2022 03:41:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 3 Mar 2022 03:55:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 19 Jul 2022 05:06:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-17"}
