d scheme is suitable for homodyne systems,\nsuch as polarization multiplexed carrier based self-homodyne links.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Feb 2022 06:18:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-21"}
